<item>
            <title>[SOLR-10948] Extraction contrib doesn&apos;t format dates properly when using DatePointField</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-10948</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SolrContentHandler has a hard coded assumption about TrieDateField that causes it to fail if you attempt to use it w/o DatePointField &amp;#8211; because it passes the Date as a string in the incorrect format.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A workaround is to explicitly configure the ParseDateFieldUpdateProcessorFactory for any field using the DatePointsField type&lt;/p&gt;</description>
